data.description: Rarely Available 3 Bed 1.1 bath townhouse is Park Ridge! Lives like a "Single Family Home" 3-Level living space. Finished Basement. Eat-In Kitchen. All Bedrooms Upstairs.  Ample Closet Space. Very large Living room/Dining room, great for entertaining. Eat-In Kitchen with table space leads to back patio for outdoor space. Large Front Patio as well.  Full finished basement with loads of storage New reassessed lighting. Off street parking out back door. Conveniently located to everything...Schools, Parks, Pools, Shopping, Restaurants, Expressways, Blue Line (to downtown & O'Hare), Airport and more! Great, Award-Winning Schools! Awesome Park District! Professionally Managed Complex. Low Monthly Assessments. Soundproof windows. New Features include , lighting throughout, hot water tank,  heating and AC.
